Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.http.api.service.mapping.annotations.methods

Annotation Type Header

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Repeatable(Headers.class)
@Target(METHOD)
public @interface Header
    Marks methods of HttpAPI. It defines http constant headers (such as 'Content-Type') of resulted http request. HeaderParameter is recommended to use when value is variable.
